            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>What's New in 1.4.0</h2>
                <h3>Added</h3><ul>
<li>Clipboard History tab: recent cleaned clips are saved locally and can be re-copied with one click, with per-item delete and Clear All</li>
<li>"Remember cleaned clips" setting to enable/disable history</li>
</ul>
<h3>Changed</h3><ul>
<li>Reorganized the popover into Settings and History tabs with an iOS-style segmented control</li>
<li>The "Clear Formatting Now" button is always visible above the tabs</li>
</ul>
            ]]></description>
